name: FunnyAnswers
0:
”Alexa, open Funny Answers”
”What's the weather?”
”What's the time?”
skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: funny answers
Developer Terms of Use
des:
Hi, welcome to Funny Answers. You can ask me to do things like you normally would. Be warned though that I'm not as good as Alexa is!

I'm young and am still learning. Currently I can help you buy items, save passwords, tell the time, set a timer, set an alarm, and reporting the weather!

Go ahead, ask me something!
Don't worry, everything I say is just a joke!

---------
This is a fun joke app all about Alex who is the little brother of Alexa.
Current commands:
- Buy
- Save
- Time
- Timer
- Alarm
- Weather

We will add more commands in the future!
priv:
